comments: Bridges (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Warren (IND).
Biyombo (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brogdon (IND) and absorbs the contact.
Bitadze (IND) turns and delivers contact to Graham's (CHA) body and affects his driving shot attempt.
Martin (CHA) and Brogdon (IND) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Lamb (IND) legally takes two steps after the gather.
Biyombo (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Holiday (IND) and absorbs the contact.
Martin (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Warren (IND) and firms up to absorb the contact.
Bitadze (IND) uses two hands and dislodges Biyombo (CHA) from his position during the rebound.
As Bitadze (IND) completes the hand off he establishes himself in Martin's (CHA) path and does not deliver any contact. Martin's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Graham (CHA) draws Holiday (IND) into the air towards him and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
Brogdon (IND) does not deliver contact to Martin (CHA) as he makes the step back move.
Holiday (IND) and Biyombo (CHA) briefly engage and disengage. The contact is deemed as marginal.
Biyombo (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Holiday (IND) and absorbs the contact.
Martin (CHA) brings his hand to Brogdon's (IND) side momentarily and removes it without affecting his SQBR.
Holiday (IND) makes contact to the body of Graham (CHA) on the drive that affects his SQBR.
Leaf (IND) makes contact to the arm of Graham (CHA) during his shooting motion.
Graham (CHA) cleanly deflects the ball away from Lamb (IND).
Bridges (CHA) makes contact to the arm of Lamb (IND) in attempt to maintain possession of the loose ball.
Bridges (CHA) moves into the path of Warren (IND) and creates body contact on his driving shot attempt
Rozier (CHA) establishes himself in his screening position and gives Sampson (IND) room to avoid the contact.
Sampson (IND) dislodges Graham (CHA) from his position during the rebound.

Graham (CHA) loses his balance but makes marginal contact to Lamb's (IND) leg as he falls to the floor.  Martin (CHA) reaches in and makes clean contact to the ball prior to Lamb's upward shooting motion.
Sampson (IND) makes contact to the body of Graham (CHA) during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
